{"tid":1263240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥 今鋪比你搞到好想自殺！","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:21:22.000Z","uid":12034,"like":159,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"564b33a304eed5f3294eec2b69977181a1710ad6","tid":1263240,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"上年同班啲同學都有玩手遊<br />\n咁佢地玩開神魔 有次我就同佢地講 唔好玩神抄啦 <br />\n抄人野 要玩玩pad 支持下原創<br />\n又推介暴擊英雄比佢地玩 佢地笑我on9<br />\n自此就杯我 又成日玩我<br />\n<br />\n點知 早幾日比人爆大獲<br />\n原來你隻game都係抄人! <br />\n我而家係咁比佢地笑抄game仔 老翻仔 不是正版仔<br />\n你肯出聲未? 點對得住我地班兄弟?<br />\n難為我地仲課金支持你 <br />\n我兩日lunch錢 變左好似比錢支持侵權咁!<br />\n<br />\n而家一打開電話就比人笑 <br />\n就黎受唔住 想死左一了百了<br />\n你到底仲想龜縮到幾時?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://upload.cc/i1/2019/04/28/YtgTG1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2FYtgTG1.png&h=1d00033f&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ROXT72L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROXT72L.png&h=7271d38b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1475bba1566edd11c18f7264ce891dcf2f307187","tid":1263240,"uid":112416,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"致敬啫，好似係"},{"pid":"44e50ce037039dd882368e17c34720d93091fec9","tid":1263240,"uid":251052,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"ching唔好為咗個賣港賊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6805e18384110cfe26240ae93a40e7b37f06a64d","tid":1263240,"uid":8968,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"44e50ce037039dd882368e17c34720d93091fec9","tid":1263240,"uid":251052,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"ching唔好為咗個賣港賊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/